data.description: Presenting a stunning brand new condominium in Anthem for 55 and up in a gated community. Each building has secured entry, elevators for easy access and a courtyard to enjoy. This 2 BR, 2 BA sits in over 1500 sq ft with an open concept. The kitchen boasts all stainless steel appliances, quartz countertop, a pantry, and endless cabinet space.  Ceiling fans in Living room & Master BR. Motion detection lights in hallway BR, laundry RM, including in the 2 CAR Tandem garage. The balcony is just off of the dining area where you can enjoy a tranquil moment with mountain views. The community features a stunning clubhouse, a resort style pool and spa, a fitness room, activity room for relaxation or group activities. Just walking distance from the community is the Revere golf club where you can enjoy golf year round. The community has very active calendar of events from dancing, card games, hiking and wine tasting. Community has charging stations for electric vehicles. This community has it all.
